#. <section class="sutta" id="sn47.25"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn47.25:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 47"
msgstr "Linked Discourses 47"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "sn47.25:0.2"
msgid "3. Sīlaṭṭhitivagga"
msgstr "3. Ethics and Duration"

#. </p><h1>
#. VAR: 25. Aññatarabrāhmaṇasutta → brāhmaṇasuttaṃ (bj) | brāhmaṇa (pts1)
msgctxt "sn47.25:0.3"
msgid "25. Aññatarabrāhmaṇasutta"
msgstr "25. A Certain Brahmin"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "sn47.25:1.1"
msgid "Evaṃ me sutaṃ—​"
msgstr "So I have heard."

msgctxt "sn47.25:1.2"
msgid ""
"ekaṃ samayaṃ bhagavā sāvatthiyaṃ viharati jetavane anāthapiṇḍikassa ārāme."
msgstr ""
"At one time the Buddha was staying near Sāvatthī in Jeta’s Grove, "
"Anāthapiṇḍika’s monastery."

msgctxt "sn47.25:1.3"
msgid ""
"Atha kho aññataro brāhmaṇo yena bhagavā tenupasaṅkami; upasaṅkamitvā "
"bhagavatā saddhiṃ sammodi."
msgstr ""
"Then a certain brahmin went up to the Buddha, and exchanged greetings with "
"him."

msgctxt "sn47.25:1.4"
msgid ""
"Sammodanīyaṃ kathaṃ sāraṇīyaṃ vītisāretvā ekamantaṃ nisīdi. Ekamantaṃ "
"nisinno kho so brāhmaṇo bhagavantaṃ etadavoca:"
msgstr ""
"When the greetings and polite conversation were over, he sat down to one "
"side and said to the Buddha:"

msgctxt "sn47.25:1.5"
msgid ""
"“ko nu kho, bho gotama, hetu, ko paccayo yena tathāgate parinibbute "
"saddhammo na ciraṭṭhitiko hoti?"
msgstr ""
"“What is the cause, Master Gotama, what is the reason why the true teaching "
"does not last long after the final extinguishment of the Realized One?"

msgctxt "sn47.25:1.6"
msgid ""
"Ko pana, bho gotama, hetu, ko paccayo yena tathāgate parinibbute saddhammo "
"ciraṭṭhitiko hotī”ti?"
msgstr ""
"And what is the cause, what is the reason why the true teaching does last "
"long after the final extinguishment of the Realized One?”"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "sn47.25:2.1"
msgid ""
"“Catunnaṃ kho, brāhmaṇa, satipaṭṭhānānaṃ abhāvitattā abahulīkatattā "
"tathāgate parinibbute saddhammo na ciraṭṭhitiko hoti."
msgstr ""
"“Brahmin, it’s because of not developing and cultivating the four kinds of "
"mindfulness meditation that the true teaching doesn’t last long after the "
"final extinguishment of the Realized One."

msgctxt "sn47.25:2.2"
msgid ""
"Catunnañca kho, brāhmaṇa, satipaṭṭhānānaṃ bhāvitattā bahulīkatattā tathāgate "
"parinibbute saddhammo ciraṭṭhitiko hoti."
msgstr ""
"It’s because of developing and cultivating the four kinds of mindfulness "
"meditation that the true teaching does last long after the final "
"extinguishment of the Realized One."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc3"></a>
msgctxt "sn47.25:3.1"
msgid "Katamesaṃ catunnaṃ?"
msgstr "What four?"

msgctxt "sn47.25:3.2"
msgid ""
"Idha, brāhmaṇa, bhikkhu kāye kāyānupassī viharati ātāpī sampajāno satimā, "
"vineyya loke abhijjhādomanassaṃ;"
msgstr ""
"It’s when a mendicant meditates by observing an aspect of the body—keen, "
"aware, and mindful, rid of desire and aversion for the world."

msgctxt "sn47.25:3.3"
msgid "vedanāsu … pe …"
msgstr "They meditate observing an aspect of feelings …"

msgctxt "sn47.25:3.4"
msgid "citte … pe …"
msgstr "mind …"

msgctxt "sn47.25:3.5"
msgid ""
"dhammesu dhammānupassī viharati ātāpī sampajāno satimā, vineyya loke "
"abhijjhādomanassaṃ."
msgstr ""
"principles—keen, aware, and mindful, rid of desire and aversion for the "
"world."

msgctxt "sn47.25:3.6"
msgid ""
"Imesaṃ kho, brāhmaṇa, catunnaṃ satipaṭṭhānānaṃ abhāvitattā abahulīkatattā "
"tathāgate parinibbute saddhammo na ciraṭṭhitiko hoti."
msgstr ""
"It’s because of not developing and cultivating these four kinds of "
"mindfulness meditation that the true teaching doesn’t last long after the "
"final extinguishment of the Realized One."

msgctxt "sn47.25:3.7"
msgid ""
"Imesañca kho, brāhmaṇa, catunnaṃ satipaṭṭhānānaṃ bhāvitattā bahulīkatattā "
"tathāgate parinibbute saddhammo ciraṭṭhitiko hotī”ti."
msgstr ""
"It’s because of developing and cultivating these four kinds of mindfulness "
"meditation that the true teaching does last long after the final "
"extinguishment of the Realized One.”"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc4"></a>
msgctxt "sn47.25:4.1"
msgid "Evaṃ vutte, so brāhmaṇo bhagavantaṃ etadavoca:"
msgstr "When he said this, the brahmin said to the Buddha:"

msgctxt "sn47.25:4.2"
msgid "“abhikkantaṃ, bho gotama … pe …"
msgstr "“Excellent, Master Gotama! Excellent! …"

msgctxt "sn47.25:4.3"
msgid ""
"upāsakaṃ maṃ bhavaṃ gotamo dhāretu ajjatagge pāṇupetaṃ saraṇaṃ gatan”ti."
msgstr ""
"From this day forth, may Master Gotama remember me as a lay follower who has "
"gone for refuge for life.”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn47.25:4.4"
msgid "Pañcamaṃ."
msgstr ""
